column8: Partly cloudy. Areas of fog about the ranges early this morning. Slight (30%) chance of drizzle in the morning and early afternoon. The chance of a thunderstorm with little or no rainfall about the ranges during this afternoon and evening. Winds northeast to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h becoming light in the evening. Daytime maximum temperatures between 18 and 23.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h increasing to 35 km/h before turning west to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the afternoon and evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 10 and 13 with daytime temperatures reaching 22 to 29.

Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers about the ranges, medium (50%) chance elsewhere. Winds southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting east to southeasterly during the morning then becoming easterly 25 to 35 km/h during the day. Overnight temperatures falling to between 6 and 9 with daytime temperatures reaching between 12 and 17.

Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. The chance of a thunderstorm in the afternoon and evening. Winds northeast to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h decreasing to 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 7 and 10 with daytime temperatures reaching between 15 and 19.
